{"tid":510192,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"復合根本係弱智既行為","createTime":"2017-12-26T08:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T14:13:47.000Z","uid":50351,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"980f8681d7bb56b9dafcde56bad190596cdc42c4","tid":510192,"uid":50351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"成撚日俾人洗腦咩大家變成熟再係返埋一齊<br />\n講到復合失而復得咁好撚唯美浪漫<br />\n大家經歷波瀾轉折終於再次係係埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醒下啦，復合只係D一開始對感情就唔認真既人先會做既野<br />\n一個一開始就諗住廝守終身既人，邊有可能再有信心投放自己係段曾經破裂過既關係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你就唔撚驚佢放得一次唔敢拋棄你第二次?<br />\n<br />\n好馬不吃回頭草，一個真心愛你想同你過世既人，係唔會放棄你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有咩咪一五一十拆掂佢，人地未玩夠你就放佢出去俾佢玩夠自己再做保底條友。對方已經絕左情，佢再對你動情，你都諗下個風險啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做第二次決定個陣，你估佢仲會煩惱咩"},{"pid":"ada3f03e86bba892239ecb9b725fbbec0fadf919","tid":510192,"uid":150561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:26:52.000Z","msg":"佢連機會都冇俾我就散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b540a928dfe33eb36a3f11cfc4946f30cb8add","tid":510192,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"你條女同左人復合？"},{"pid":"7cdfd1356999101aba03c5ab3e1d6f79c9ef945c","tid":510192,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ada3f03e86bba892239ecb9b725fbbec0fadf919","tid":510192,"uid":150561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:26:52.000Z","msg":"佢連機會都冇俾我就散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:29:14.000Z","msg":"好事黎<br />\n當你見到 分